---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-bg-border px-6 py-14 md:px-10 lg:px-16">
  <div class="container-page !px-0">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <img src="/icon.png" alt="" class="h-9 w-9 rounded-lg opacity-90" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold">Paraguacraft</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Launcher Minecraft Java · Tauri v2 + Rust</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          Proyecto open-source para jugar con amigos. No afiliado a Mojang AB ni Microsoft.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500">Descargar</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li><a href="/download" class="hover:text-white transition">Instalador Windows</a></li>
          <li><a href="/latest.json" class="hover:text-white transition">latest.json</a></li>
          <li><a href="/status" class="hover:text-white transition">Estado del release</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500">Proyecto</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li><a href="https://github.com/SantiJ10/Paraguacraft" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-white transition">GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/SantiJ10/Paraguacraft/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-white transition">Releases</a></li>
          <li><a href="/notas" class="hover:text-white transition">Notas de versión</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/SantiJ10/Paraguacraft/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-white transition">Reportar bug</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/SantiJ10/Paraguacraft/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-white transition">Changelog completo</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 border-t border-bg-border pt-8 text-xs text-gray-600 md:flex-row">
      <p>© {year} Paraguacraft</p>
      <p>Minecraft es marca de Mojang Synergies AB</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
